(1, 'API Betta Food', 'https://i.imgur.com/uePdyIl.jpg', 6.99, 'Formulated to enhance Betta fish colors and support overall health.', 'API Betta Food is an essential product specially designed to enhance the colors and health of Betta fish. This food is crafted using high-quality ingredients to ensure that Betta fish receive the necessary nutrients for their overall health and well-being. The primary goal of this product is to promote vibrant coloration, making the Betta fish look more stunning and alive in the aquarium. It provides a balanced mix of proteins, vitamins, and minerals, helping Betta fish stay strong and active. API Betta Food also supports immune health, reducing the risk of disease and ensuring that Betta fish thrive in their environment. The small, easily digestible pellets are specifically tailored to the unique needs of Betta fish, encouraging easy consumption. This product is ideal for any Betta fish owner who desires to maintain a healthy and beautiful fish that shows off its true colors. Whether used for daily feeding or as part of a balanced diet, API Betta Food guarantees optimal nutrition, promoting overall health, and enhancing the Bettas appearance.', 120, 'Betta Food', 47),
