(4, 'Aqueon PURE Betta', 'https://i.imgur.com/IBQQeKD.jpg', 5.49, 'Nutrient-rich food that promotes vibrant color and well-being in Betta fish.', 'Aqueon PURE Betta food is a premium product created to promote the vibrant color and overall health of Betta fish. This nutrient-rich food is made with high-quality ingredients that support long-term well-being, growth, and vitality. Aqueon PURE Betta food contains a special blend of fishmeal and proteins, making it highly digestible and perfect for Betta fish. The food is also packed with essential vitamins and minerals, which help to boost the immune system, support healthy skin and scales, and maintain good digestive health. This food is formulated to bring out the natural colors of Betta fish while keeping them active and strong. Betta fish owners will appreciate the benefits of Aqueon PURE Betta food, as it provides a well-rounded diet that ensures their fish are healthy, beautiful, and energetic. Aqueon PURE Betta is perfect for everyday feeding, offering Betta fish the necessary nutrients for a thriving and colorful life.', 150, 'Betta Food', 264),
