(9, 'Fritz Aquatics Betta Botanicals', 'https://i.imgur.com/jEXfvpW.jpg', 6.29, 'Botanically-enriched food that enhances color and provides health benefits for Betta fish.', ' Fritz Aquatics Betta Botanicals is a premium, botanically-enriched food designed to improve the health and appearance of Betta fish. This specialized formula combines the power of natural botanicals with high-quality ingredients, providing a unique blend of nutrients to enhance both coloration and vitality. The botanical ingredients in this food offer numerous health benefits, including immune system support and improved digestion, ensuring that Betta fish stay healthy and strong. The food is also designed to encourage vibrant, rich colors by supplying essential minerals and vitamins that promote the natural pigments of Betta fish. In addition to supporting coloration, Betta Botanicals also helps to bring out the Bettas natural behavior, keeping the fish active and engaged. Fritz Aquatics Betta Botanicals is perfect for Betta fish owners who want to provide their pets with a well-rounded, nutritious diet that boosts health and enhances beauty. With its easy-to-digest formula and natural ingredients, this food is an excellent choice for promoting the long-term well-being of Betta fish.', 79, 'Betta Food', 112),
